features.signature_text: Welcome to our metaverse agency "Myibiza.estate", where you can find some of our products and services. leave your details here

features.text:
MyIbiza.estate is a real estate company specializing in property management on Ibiza Island.

Our company offers a global service from property management to real estate tax consultancy.

If you are looking for a property to buy or for investment, Myibiza.estate will follow you in the search by finding the best property for you and your portfolio. We are pleased to present you a wide selection of villas, apartments, business premises or land throughout the island.

Our Professional team advise you throughout the entire sales or rental process, handling any kind of legal advice or permits required ,accordly to the local laws.

It is time to invest and take the first steps in these new worlds that will become the new frontier lands just as happened during the discovery of the Americas.

MyMetaLand.Estate offers various consulting services to enter the new world of Real Estate and Digital Lands, supporting the customer to provide with all the tools of the crypto / blockchain to be ready to start their experience in the Metaverse.

We have the ability to build tailor-made services , not only give the necessary tools, but above all, through a market analysis, direct the customer towards the correct metaverse and on which Digital Lands to jump in.

A Virtual Real Estate Agency service, 100% aligned with new trends, which are bringing out new worlds and giving new investment opportunities through interactive social systems and new economies.

The experience of the team comes from the real estate world and from the NFT and Crypto / Blockchain innovation world, giving you the right mix of skills to guarantee you adequate advice in the process of approaching the Metaverses.

MyIbiza.Estate has a long background focused on real estate brokerage in Ibiza and Balearic Islands (Spain) plus on the other side the technological and innovative experience carried out since 2014 in the crypto, NFT, blockchain world through decentralization projects.
